# Terraform Azure App Service and App Service Plan Configuration

This Terraform configuration sets up an Azure App Service Plan and an App Service. The configuration uses input variables to allow customization of the resources.

## Prerequisites

- [Terraform](https://www.terraform.io/downloads.html) installed
- An Azure account with appropriate permissions
- Azure CLI installed and authenticated (`az login`)

## Files

- `main.tf`: The main Terraform configuration file that defines the resources.
- `variables.tf`: The file that defines the input variables.
- `terraform.tfvars`: The file that provides values for the input variables.

## Usage

### 1. Clone the Repository

Clone this repository to your local machine.

```bash
git clone <repository_url>
cd <repository_directory>
